Figure Repository

This directory stores all the visual results supporting the Fractal Bubble Universe model.

Rotation_Curves/: Galaxy rotation curve comparisons between MOND and the fractal model.

CMB_Spectra/: Simulated and observed Cosmic Microwave Background power spectra.

Topology_Plots/: Visualizations of the fractal bubble wall geometry.

Note: High-resolution source files (e.g.,  .svg  or  .pdf ) are preferred for academic publishing.
